Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,（维吉尼亚州匡蒂科附近森林）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,《沉默的羔羊》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Starling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,克劳福要见你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Crawford wants to see you in his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,（伤害）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,（苦难）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,（痛苦）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,（喜欢它）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-克丽丝　-你好\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Clarice. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,（行为科学组）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,找克劳福吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Looking for Crawford?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:05:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他快回来了，在他的办公室等一会吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He should be back soon. Why don't you wait in his office?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,（比尔剥下第五个人的皮）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-克丽丝，早安　-早安，克劳福先生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Clarice M. Good morning. - Morning, Mr. Crawford.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉突然把你召离课堂\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sorry to pull you off the course at such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你的导师说你是班里的高材生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Your instructors say you're in the top quarter of your class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,希望是吧，他们还没有公布成绩\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I hope so. They haven't posted any grades yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个任务要办，于是我想起你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}A job's come up, and I thought about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是正式的任务，较像一份有趣的差事\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Not a job, really, more of an interesting errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你出席过，我在维吉尼亚大学的讲座\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I remember you from my seminar at UVA.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你追问我本局在胡佛年代的，公民权益记录\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You grilled me on the bureau's civil rights record in the Hoover years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我给了你甲等\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I gave you an A.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是甲下\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}A minus, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,双主修，心理学及犯罪学，以优异成绩毕业\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Double major, psych and criminology, graduated magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在瑞辛格疗养院做过夏季实习\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Summer internships at the Reitzinger Clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,它说你毕业后，想在行为科学组替我工作\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It says when you graduate you want to work for me in Behavioral Science.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我很想\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, very much, sir. Very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在访问被囚禁的连环杀手\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We're interviewing all serial killers in custody...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,作变态行为的分析\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}for a psycho-behavioral profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,对一些悬案会有很大帮助\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It could be a real help in unsolved cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们大都乐意跟我们谈\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Most of them have been happy to talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你会否很易受惊的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Do you spook easily, Starling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Not yet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最想见的那个人拒绝合作\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The one we want most refuses to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你去精神病院找他\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I want you to go after him in the asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人是谁？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Who's the subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-心理医生汉尼拔・莱达　-食人狂魔汉尼拔\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- The psychiatrist, Hannibal Lecter. - "Hannibal the Cannibal."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他不会跟你交谈\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I don't expect him to talk to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但无论如何我们都得尝试\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}but I have to be able to say we tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,若他不合作，我要如实报告\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}If he won't cooperate, I want straight reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他的容貌和监狱里的状况如何？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}How's he look? How's his cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他有没有素描，绘画？如果有，他都画些什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Is he sketching, drawing? If he is, what's he sketching?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是莱达的档案...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Here's a dossier on Lecter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,问卷副本和你的身份证\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}copy of our questionnaire and an I.D. for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,周三早上八点把你的报告交给我\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Have your memo on my desk by 0800, Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，为什么这样急？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Excuse me, sir, but why the urgency?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达已经坐牢很多年了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lecter's been in prison for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他和水牛比尔是否有关连？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Is there some connection between him and Buffalo Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿有，我要你非常留意\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I wish there were. Now, I want your full attention, Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-知道　-要非常小心应付汉尼拔・莱达\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Yes, sir. - Be very careful with Hannibal Lecter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,精神病院的奇顿医生，会给你讲解接见程序\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Chilton at the asylum will go over all the physical procedures used.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何不可偏离程序\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Do not deviate from them for any reason whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可向他透露私人事情\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You're to tell him nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想汉尼拔・莱达知道你的思想的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You don't want Hannibal Lecter inside your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,执行你的任务，但千万别忘记他的身份\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Just do your job but never forget what he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个魔头，一个变态狂人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, he's a monster, a pure psychopath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可以生擒一个已很难得了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It's so rare to capture one alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,从研究角度来说，莱达是我们最有价值的资产\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}From a research point of view, Lecter is our most prized asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有很多探员来这里的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We get a lot of detectives here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但我记不起有这样漂亮的一个\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}but I must say I can't remember one as attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你会在巴尔的摩过夜吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Will you be in Baltimore overnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有适当的向导，这可以是个很好玩的城市\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Because this can be quite a fun town if you have the right guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定这是个了不起的城市\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm sure this is a great town, Dr. Chilton...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但我要见莱达医生，下午还要回去报告\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}but I must talk to Dr. Lecter and report back this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，那么我们快点吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I see. Well, let's make this quick, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们尝试研究他，但他太高深了，一般的测试都不适用\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We've tried to study him, but he's too sophisticated for the standard tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他很讨厌我们的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, my, does he hate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他觉得我是他的报应\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He thinks I'm his nemesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,克劳福真是聪明，他利用你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Crawford's very clever, isn't he, using you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么意思？　-找个漂亮的女郎来引诱他\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- What do you mean, sir? - Pretty young woman to turn him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信这八年来莱达都没见过女人，而你正合他的胃口\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I don't believe Lecter's seen a woman in eight years, and you are his taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}So to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我毕业于维吉尼亚大学，它不是一间仪态学校\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I graduated from UVA. It's not a charm school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，你该能记着那些规矩了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Good. Then you should be able to remember the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不要触摸或接近那块玻璃，只可传递柔软的纸张给他\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Do not touch or approach the glass. Pass him nothing but soft paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不可有铅笔或原子笔，纸张上不可有钉书钉或夹子\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No pencils or pens, no staples or paper clips in his paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只可用那个活动食物架传送\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Use the sliding food carrier, no exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不可接受他给你的东西\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}If he passes you anything, do not accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-明白吗？　-明白\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Do you understand? - Yes, I understand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你看看，为何我们要有这些戒备\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm going to show you why we insist on such precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在1981年7月8日的下午\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}On the afternoon of July 8, 1981...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他说胸口痛，被带往医疗室\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}he complained of chest pains and was taken to the dispensary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为方便做心电图，他的口罩被除下\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}His mouthpiece was removed for an EKG.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,当护士靠近他身边时，他对她做了这个\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}When the nurse leaned over him, he did this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,医生们算是重整了她的下颚，救回她一只眼睛\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The doctors managed to reset her jaw, more or less. Save one of her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,即使在他吃她的舌头时，他的脉搏从没超过85\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}His pulse never got above 85, even when he ate her tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-我把他关在这里　-奇顿医生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- I keep him in here. - Dr. Chilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,若莱达觉得你是他的敌人，那么...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}If Lecter feels that you're his enemy, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,若我单独去的话，我们运气可能会好一点\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Maybe we'll have more luck if I go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为如何？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你若在我办公室时提出来，就可省掉我的时间了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You might have suggested this in my office and saved me the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，但我会错过了和你同行的乐趣\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, sir, but then I would have missed the pleasure of your company, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她完事后带她出去吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}When she's finished, bring her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，我是巴尼，他说过了，不要走近那块玻璃\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hi, I'm Barney. He told you, don't get near the glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对，他说过了，我是克丽丝・史达琳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, he did. Clarice Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,幸会，你可以把大衣挂在那里\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Nice to meet you. You can hang your coat there if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，谢谢你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay. Thank you, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他在最尽头的那个牢房\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He's past the others. The last cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,靠右走吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You keep to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-我放了一张椅子给你　-很好，谢谢你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- I put out a chair for you. - Yes, that's very good, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我会看着，你不会有事的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'll be watching. You'll do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以闻到你的私处\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I can smell your cunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,早安\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生，我叫克丽丝・史达琳，可否跟你谈一会？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Lecter, my name is Clarice Starling. May I speak with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是克劳福的人，是吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You're one of Jack Crawford's, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I am, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可否看看你的证件？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}May I see your credentials?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近一点，劳烦你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Closer, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,近一点\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一周内后就到期了，你不是真的联邦调查局探员吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That expires in one week. You're not real FBI, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我仍在受训\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm still in training at the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-克劳福派个见习生来见我？　-是的，我是个学生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Jack Crawford sent a trainee to me? - Yes, I'm a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来向你学习的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm here to learn from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你可以决定，我是否够资格这样做\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Maybe you can decide if I'm qualified enough to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你很不老实呢，史达琳探员\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That is rather slippery of you, Agent Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sit. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我，迈克斯对你说了什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Now then, tell me. What did Miggs say to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,隔壁的“多面人迈克斯”\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}"Multiple Miggs" in the next cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他向你发出嘶嘶声，他说了些什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He hissed at you. What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他说“我可以闻到你的私处”\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He said, "I can smell your cunt."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我可闻不到\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I myself cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你用爱肤恩润肤膏\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You use Evyan skin cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有时你会涂点香水\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And sometimes you wear L'Air du Temps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但今天没有\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}But not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这些画是你画的吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Did you do all these drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:15:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那是从观景楼远望的大教堂\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That is the Duomo, seen from the Belvedere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道佛罗伦斯吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Do you know Florence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那些细节都是来自记忆的吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}All that detail just from memory, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳探员，我只有记忆，没有景观\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Memory, Agent Starling, is what I have instead of a view.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你可在这份问卷上，给我们一些见解\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Perhaps you'd care to lend us your view on this questionnaire, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不...你做得很好\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No, no, no. You were doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你很有礼，而且能容纳礼貌\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You had been courteous and receptive to courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你对迈克斯的尴尬说话，也表现得很信任\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You had established trust with the embarrassing truth about Miggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,至于你这份拙劣的问卷\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And now this ham-handed segue into your questionnaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就不行了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是要求你看看它，你做不做随便你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm only asking you to look at this. Either you will or you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对，若克劳福要从学校找人帮忙\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah. Jack Crawford must be very busy indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定很忙了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}if he's recruiting help from the student body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,忙于追捕那个新手水牛比尔吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Busy hunting that new one, Buffalo Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他真是个坏孩子\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What a naughty boy he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你可知道为何他，被称为水牛比尔？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Do you know why he's called "Buffalo Bill"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我，报纸上没有说\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Please tell me. The newspapers won't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是来自堪萨斯城，凶案组的一个笑话\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It started as a joke in Kansas City Homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说“这个人喜欢剥他猎物的皮”\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They said, "This one likes to skin his humps."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳探员，你认为为什么...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Why do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他要剥她们的皮？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}he removes their skins, Agent Starling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的敏锐来振奋我一下吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thrill me with your acumen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做令他兴奋\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It excites him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大部分的连环杀手都会保存受害人身上的东西作为纪念品\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Most serial killers keep trophies from their victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-我可没有　-对\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- I didn't. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃了他们\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No, you ate yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,把那个传过来吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You send that through now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为凭这份拙劣的东西，便可以分析我？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You think you can dissect me with this blunt little tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是！我相信你的学识...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No! I thought that your knowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你很有野心，是不是？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You're so ambitious, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可知道你拿着那个高级皮包，穿着廉价鞋子像个什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You know what you look like, with your good bag and your cheap shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,像个土包子\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You look like a rube.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一个干净，忙碌，带点品味的土包子\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}A well-scrubbed, hustling rube with a little taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你衣食无忧地成长...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Nutrition has given you some length of bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你不外乎是个白种低下层的人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}but you're not more than one generation from white trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是，史达琳探员？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}are you, Agent Starling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你极力想摆脱口音...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The accent you've tried so desperately to shed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,地道的西维吉尼亚州腔调\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}pure West Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲是个矿工吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Is your father a coal miner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那盏灯可有令他满身臭气？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Does he stink of the lamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道那些男孩怎样迅速搭上你，在汽车后座里乱摸\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I know how quickly the boys found you, all those tedious, sticky fumblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你却想着走出去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}in the back seats of cars, while you dreamed of getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,走去天涯海角\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Getting anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,直走到联邦调查局\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Getting all the way to the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你很有观察力\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You see a lot, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但你能否用你敏锐的观察力...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}But are you strong enough to point that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来分析自己？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}high-powered perception at yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不如你探究一下自己，把观察所得写下来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Why don't you look at yourself and write down what you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你害怕这样做吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Or maybe you're afraid to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经有一个人口调查员想测试我\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}A census taker once tried to test me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他的肝配蚕豆吃了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I ate his liver with some fava beans...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还有美味的红酒呢\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and a nice Chianti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小史达琳，你飞回学校去吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You fly back to school now, little Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,飞吧...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Fly, fly, fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我咬我的手腕...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I bit my wrist...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才能死掉\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}so I could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看这些血\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Look at the blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,吓到你了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克斯！你这个混蛋！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Miggs! You stupid fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳探员！回来！史达琳探员\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Agent Starling! Come back! Agent Starling! Agent Starling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让那种事情再发生，我讨厌不礼貌的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I would not have had that happen. Discourtesy is ugly to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-那么做这个测验吧　-不做，但我会令你开心的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Then do this test! - No, but I will make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-我会给你一个大好机会　-什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- I'll give you a chance at your love. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,升职，听着，你自我反省一下，克丽丝・史达琳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Advancement. Listen. Look deep within yourself, Clarice Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,找出我从前的病人莫菲小姐\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Go seek out Miss Mofet, an old patient of mine. M-O-F-E-T.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信迈克斯不会这么快发作的...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I don't think Miggs could manage again so soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他是疯的，快去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}even though he is crazy. Go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，比尔\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hi, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-爸爸　-克丽丝\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Daddy! - Hey, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-爸爸，你有没有抓到坏人？　-没有，他们跑掉了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Did you get any bad guys, Daddy? - No, angel. They all got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Ah, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局，举手，别动！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}FBI! Hands up! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,转过身来，把双手放在后面，好的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Turn around. Hands behind your back. Thumbs up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳，你已经死了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You're dead, Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,强生，进入和指挥都做得很好，史达琳，你哪里有危险？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Johnson, good entry, good command. Starling, where's your danger area?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-在角落　-你有没有检查过它？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- In the corner. - Did you check it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-没有，长官　-所以你已经死了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- No, sir. - That's why you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,3109？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}3-1-0-9?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,打破门或窗闯入或者撤退\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Breaking doors or windows to enter or exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,404号规条呢？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Rule 404?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,（巴尔的摩心理医生，获得最高荣誉）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,（著名心理医生被控谋杀）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,（食人狂魔审讯带来新的恐怖）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽丝，你的电话，是教官\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Clarice, phone. It's the guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,克劳福？谢谢，雅戴\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Crawford? Thanks, Ardelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-史达琳？　-长官\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Starling? - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克斯死了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Miggs is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,死了？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎会的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,守卫听到汉尼拔・莱达下午时对他低声说话\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The orderly heard Lecter whispering to him all afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在夜间巡查时，发现他吞掉自己的舌头\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They found him at bed check. He'd swallowed his tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Starling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在听，我只是...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah. I'm still here, sir. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道对这件事该有何感想\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I don't know how to feel about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用感想什么，莱达这样做只是为了自娱\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You don't have to feel any way. Lecter did it to amuse himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白今天很难受\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Look, I know it got ugly today...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但你提到莫菲，有后续行动吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}but you mentioned a name, "Mofet." Any follow-up on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他在被捕前，把大部分病人的病历销毁了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He destroyed most of his patients' histories prior to capture...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没有莫菲的记录\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}so there's no record of anyone named Mofet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得“你自己”这个参考资料，对莱达来说太造作了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}But I thought the "yourself' reference was too hokey for Lecter...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起他是来自巴尔的摩，便翻查电话簿\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}so I figured he's from Baltimore, and I looked in the phone book.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有一间叫“你自己”的自助式仓库\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And there's a "Your Self' storage facility...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.05,0:22:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在巴尔的摩市外围\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}right outside of downtown Baltimore, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.76,0:22:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,31号仓已经租了十年...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Unit 31 was leased...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,租金是全数预缴的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}for 10 years, prepaid in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,合约是以一个...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The contract was in the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是赫斯达・莫菲小姐的人定的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}of a Miss Hester Mofet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,自从1980年就没有人来过了？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}So nobody's been in here since 1980?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,以我所知是没有\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Not to my knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我的顾客都很重视私隐权的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Privacy is a great concern to my customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我答应不会扰乱任何东西\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, I won't disturb anything, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我很快便会离开\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'll be out of here before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-要帮忙吗？　-好的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- May I help you? - Yes, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这里\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-它被卡着　-明天可以叫我的儿子来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- It's stuck. - We could return tomorrow with my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么样？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.26,0:23:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可叫我的司机帮你，但他讨厌体力劳动\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I would ask my driver to help you, but he detests physical labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.87,0:23:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.64,0:23:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你别走开，我很快回来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You stay here. I'll be back in one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.94,0:24:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,它被卡着，请你把那支电筒给我\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It's stuck. Will you hand me that flashlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.92,0:24:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这道门跌下来...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}If this door should fall down...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.26,0:24:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,或者有什么意外...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}or anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.90,0:24:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们巴尔的摩办公室的电话号码\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}this is the number for our Baltimore office.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.70,0:24:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道你跟我在一起的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They know that you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.64,0:24:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-如果有意外就找他们吧　-好的，史达琳小姐\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Call them if anything should happen. - Yes, Miss Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.42,0:27:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽丝，他们在等你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Clarice. Here, they're waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.16,0:27:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.93,0:27:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,“赫斯达・莫菲”是拼字猜谜吧？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hester Mofet. It's an anagram, isn't it, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.17,0:27:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是“我其余的东西”\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hester Mofet: "The rest of me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.57,0:27:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那表示车库是你租的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}"Miss The Rest Of Me," meaning that you rented that garage?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.34,0:28:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.58,0:28:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你止血了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Your bleeding has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.42,0:28:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么...？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}How did...?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.59,0:28:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没有大碍的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.39,0:28:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只是皮外伤\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.42,0:28:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生，那瓶里的头颅是谁的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Lecter, whose head is in that bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.89,0:28:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你不问我，关于水牛比尔的事？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Why don't you ask me about Buffalo Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.30,0:28:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他的事？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Do you know something about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.16,0:28:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我看过档案可能知道的，你可以替我拿\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I might if I saw the case file. You could get that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.47,0:28:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谈谈莫菲小姐吧，你要我去找他\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Let's talk about Miss Mofet. You wanted me to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.57,0:28:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他的真名是班哲文・赖普，是我的前病患\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}His real name is Benjamin Raspail. A former patient of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.14,0:28:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他的恋爱对象，有点怪异\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}whose romantic attachments ran to, shall we say, the exotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.28,0:29:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有杀他，只是把他藏起来，就像我发现他时的样子\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I did not kill him, merely tucked him away, very much as I found him...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.72,0:29:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在他错过了三次约会之后\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}after he'd missed three appointments.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.32,0:29:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,若你没有杀他，那么是谁杀？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}If you didn't kill him, who did?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.79,0:29:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道？对他来说是件好事\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Who can say? Best thing for him, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.90,0:29:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他的治疗没有功效\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}His therapy was going nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.80,0:29:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他的裙子，化妆...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}His dress, makeup...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.34,0:29:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,赖普是个异性装扮癖好者？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Raspail was a transvestite?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.14,0:29:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,生活上？不是，只是普通的躁狂抑郁\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}In life? Oh, no. Garden variety manic-depressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.01,0:29:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,乏味，非常乏味\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Tedious, very tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.68,0:29:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我把他看成是一个实验\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I now think of him as an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.32,0:29:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一个没经验的杀手尝试转变\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}A fledgling killer's first effort at transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.02,0:29:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到他时有何感觉？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}How did you feel when you saw him, Clarice?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.19,0:29:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,初时很害怕，后来...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Scared at first, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.19,0:29:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,便很振奋\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}exhilarated.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.13,0:29:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,克劳福在提拔你，是吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Jack Crawford is helping your career, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.53,0:29:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你们互相倾慕呢\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Apparently, he likes you and you like him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.03,0:29:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没有想过\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I never thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.30,0:29:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为克劳福对你有遐想吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Do you think Jack Crawford wants you, sexually?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.17,0:29:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他年纪大很多，你对他可有想入非非？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He is much older, but do you think he visualizes scenarios, exchanges?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.51,0:30:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你做爱？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Fucking you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.75,0:30:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有兴趣，这是迈克斯会说的那种话\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That doesn't interest me. It's the sort of thing that Miggs would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.89,0:30:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不再是了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.03,0:30:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，巴尼\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you, Barney.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.57,0:30:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的画呢？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What happened to your drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.31,0:30:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,惩罚，为了迈克斯那件事，像那个传道节目...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Punishment, you see, for Miggs. Just like that gospel program.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.91,0:30:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你离开后他们就会调高声音\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}When you leave, they'll turn the volume way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.01,0:30:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,奇顿医生喜欢这些折磨伎俩\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Chilton does enjoy his petty torments.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.99,0:30:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你说转变是什么意思？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What did you mean by "transformation," doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.36,0:30:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽丝，我在这里八年了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I've been in this room for eight years now, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.07,0:30:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道在我有生之年，他们都不会释放我\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I know they will never ever let me out while I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.30,0:31:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要的是一个景观\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What I want is a view.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.67,0:31:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要一个看到树和水的窗户\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I want a window where I can see a tree or even water.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.68,0:31:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去一间远离奇顿医生的联邦监狱\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I want to be in a federal institution far away from Dr. Chilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.51,0:31:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你说“没经验的杀手”，是什么意思？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What did you mean by "fledgling killer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.08,0:31:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否说他已经再次杀人？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Are you saying he's killed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.22,0:31:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我根据案件的证据，给你对水牛比尔...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm offering you a psychological profile on Buffalo Bill...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.62,0:31:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,作心理分析\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}based on the case evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.90,0:31:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你抓到他\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'll help you catch him, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.04,0:31:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他是谁，是不是？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You know who he is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.98,0:31:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我谁把你的病人斩首了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Tell me who decapitated your patient, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.91,0:31:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意等待的人都有好报的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}All good things to those who wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.18,0:31:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经等了，但杰克能等多久？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I've waited, Clarice. But how long can you and old Jackie-boy wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.85,0:31:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的小比尔一定正在找寻着，下一位特别的女士了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Our little Billy must already be searching for that next special lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.89,0:32:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,（田纳西州孟斐斯市）
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.22,0:32:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小猫咪\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hey, little cheeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.73,0:33:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我快来了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.15,0:33:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.09,0:33:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要我帮忙吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Can I help you with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.90,0:33:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.06,0:33:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.93,0:33:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.97,0:33:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不用客气，你好像是伤残人士\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That's all right. You look kind of handicapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.47,0:33:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我搬到这里但搬不上货车\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah. I got it this far, I just can't get it up in the truck by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.67,0:33:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，抓着，上！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Here, grab this. Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.88,0:33:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.14,0:33:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,把它放下吧，很好\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Just set it down. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.75,0:33:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你上车，我想把它推进去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Get in the truck. I want to push it all the way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.75,0:34:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很谢谢你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I really appreciate this. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.05,0:34:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,放到后面去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Just go all the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.82,0:34:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,行了吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay. Is this good?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.89,0:34:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,行了，很好\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.16,0:34:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-真好　-好的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- That's great. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.77,0:34:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你大概穿十四号吧？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Say, are you about a size 14?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.47,0:34:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.02,0:34:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,（十四号）
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.92,0:34:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.38,0:35:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.06,0:35:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,抓着\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Holds!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.97,0:35:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.71,0:35:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Starling!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.68,0:35:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,出去，我们走吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Outside. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.55,0:35:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,仙蒂，进场代替史达琳，来吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Cindy, in the ring for Starling. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.76,0:35:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾你的装备\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Pack your field gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.26,0:35:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们会跟克劳福一起去　-去哪里？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- You're going with Crawford. - Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.17,0:35:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在西维吉尼亚，发现了一名女子尸体\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Found a girl's body in West Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.04,0:36:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她在水里一周了，看来是水牛比尔做的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Been in the water a week. Looks like Buffalo Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.52,0:36:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,（西维吉尼亚州克莱县）
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.61,0:36:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,（联邦调查局）
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.82,0:36:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,让她们活上三天，我们不明白原因\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Keeps them alive for three days. We don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.05,0:36:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,死前没有强奸或虐待的迹象\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No evidence of rape or physical abuse prior to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.36,0:36:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这些伤口都是死后造成的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}All the mutilation you see there is postmortem.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.59,0:36:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,三天...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay, three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.80,0:36:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他开枪射死她们，剥皮和弃尸\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}then he shoots them, skins them and dumps them
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.23,0:36:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,每个尸体弃置在不同的河上\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Each body in a different river.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.13,0:36:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,河水冲走了证据\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The water leaves us no trace evidence of any kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.47,0:36:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是第一个，费迪嘉・拜姆\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That's Fredrica Bimmel, the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.11,0:36:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她的尸体是唯一被他沈下去的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Her body was the only one he weighted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.18,0:36:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上，她是第三个被发现的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}So actually, she was the third girl found.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.21,0:36:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,继她之后，他变得懒惰了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}After her, he got lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.25,0:36:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，我们看看\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.22,0:36:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,圆圈是那些女子被掳走的位置，箭嘴是尸体被发现的地点\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Circles where the girls were abducted. Arrows where their bodies were found.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.62,0:36:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,今天这个被冲到这里来，在西维吉尼亚州埃尔克河被发现\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}This new one today washed up here. Elk River, West Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.35,0:37:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳，仔细看看，告诉我你有什么发现\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Look at him, Starling. Tell me what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.32,0:37:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个白种男人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Well, he's a white male.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.99,0:37:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,连环杀手倾向于在自己的族群中猎杀\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Serial killers tend to hunt within their own ethnic groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.76,0:37:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是个流浪者，他有自己的独立房子\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He's not a drifter. He's got his own house, not an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.63,0:37:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么？　-他下毒手时，需要私人地方\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Why? - What he does with them takes privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.17,0:37:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他年约三四十岁，孔武有力\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He's in his 30s or 40s. He's got real physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.80,0:37:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有中年人的自制能力，谨慎而准绳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Combined with an older man's self-control. He's cautious, precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.84,0:37:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他从来不冲动，也不会罢休\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And he's never impulsive. He'll never stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.08,0:37:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.65,0:37:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经迷上了这回事，而且越来越熟练\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He's got a real taste for it now, and he's getting better at his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.99,0:38:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不错呢，有问题吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Not bad, Starling. Questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.32,0:38:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.99,0:38:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有提及我报告里的任何资料\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You haven't mentioned anything about the information in my report...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.96,0:38:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,或者莱达医生的提议\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}or Dr. Lecter's offer, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.57,0:38:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在考虑中\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm considering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.60,0:38:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你派我去病院\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That's why you sent me in there, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.74,0:38:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,找他协助缉捕水牛比尔？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}To get his help on Buffalo Bill, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.91,0:38:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那是事实...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Well, if that was the case, then I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.78,0:38:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望可以早点知道罢了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I just wish I was in on it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.75,0:38:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,若以真正目的派你去，莱达会识破的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}If I'd sent you in there with a real agenda, Lecter would have known it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.05,0:38:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他会把你玩弄，什么也不会说\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He would have toyed with you, then turned to stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.10,0:38:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,（格里殡仪馆）
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.22,0:39:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了，柏金斯警长？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Excuse me, Sheriff Perkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.23,0:39:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是联邦调查局人员\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}These are the FBI people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.69,0:39:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,柏金斯警长，我是杰克・克劳福，这是泰瑞和史达琳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sheriff Perkins, Jack Crawford, FBI. Special Agent Terry, Agent Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.97,0:39:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢邀请我们来到你们的管辖区\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We appreciate being invited to your jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.83,0:39:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是州政府检察部找你们的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Somebody from the state attorney's office called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.30,0:39:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会通力合作，但现在...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We'll extend you every courtesy, but right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.57,0:39:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,警长\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sheriff...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.58,0:39:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为该在私底下谈论这类性罪行的细节\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}this type of sex crime has aspects I'd just as soon discuss in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.51,0:39:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吧？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.03,0:41:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,奥加，去教堂叫区医生来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oscar, fetch Dr. Akin from the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.63,0:41:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在后面这里\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We're back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.95,0:41:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,叫拉玛弹奏完毕后过来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Tell Lamar to come on when he's finished playing his music.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.30,0:41:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我们稍后会传过来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, we'll be sending in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.87,0:41:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,行了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.01,0:41:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要组成六线联系，芝加哥，底特律...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I need a six-way link up. Chicago, Detroit...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.51,0:41:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.88,0:41:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.78,0:41:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，各位警官先生，听着\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Excuse me, officers and gentlemen. Listen here, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.25,0:41:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要替她做一些事情\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}There's things we need to do for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.66,0:41:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你们把她带来了这里，她的家人会感谢...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Y'all brought her this far, and her folks would thank you if they could...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.39,0:41:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的善意和体谅\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}for your kindness and your sensitivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.20,0:42:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,请离开吧，让我们照顾她好了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Please, go on now, and let us take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.10,0:42:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Go on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.51,0:42:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.61,0:42:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.61,0:42:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.29,0:42:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，埃尔克河，准备传送\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, that's right. Elk River. Stand by for transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.10,0:42:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.58,0:42:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大家来看看她吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Doctor, Lamar. Let's take a look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.50,0:43:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Jesus...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.97,0:43:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳，行了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay, Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.70,0:43:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,胸骨上有星形的伤口\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Star-shaped contact entrance wound over the sternum.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.47,0:43:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,上面有个枪口印记\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}A muzzle stamp at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.54,0:43:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-死于非命　-死于非命\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Wrongful death. - Wrongful death.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.04,0:43:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她要被送去克拉斯顿的病理学家那里\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}She'll have to go to the state pathologist's at Claxton.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.38,0:43:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是回去那个丧礼了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Well, I better get back to that service.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.68,0:43:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,利玛会帮你们的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lamar will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.78,0:44:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lord Almighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.79,0:44:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你还观察到什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What else do you see, Starling?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.06,0:44:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是当地人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Well, she's not local.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.70,0:44:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她穿了三个耳洞，还有...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Her ears are pierced three times and there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.03,0:44:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,闪亮的指甲油，看来是城市人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}glitter nail polish. It looks like town to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.74,0:44:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她有两只指甲断了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Two of her fingernails are broken off...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.21,0:44:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,指甲下有泥土和沙粒\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and there's dirt or grit under them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.72,0:44:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她好像想爬过一些什么似的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It looks like she's tried to claw her way through something.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.29,0:44:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞，替她的牙齿拍照，稍后传真到失踪人口组\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Ray, get pictures of her teeth. We'll fax them to Missing Persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.22,0:44:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.10,0:44:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,再拍一张\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Let's do another.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.61,0:45:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她喉咙里有东西\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}She's got something in her throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.58,0:45:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当尸体被捞出水面时\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}When a body comes out of the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.88,0:45:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,口里总会有些树叶之类的东西\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}lots of times there's leaves and things in the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.98,0:45:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.38,0:45:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,豆荚吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Some kind of seedpod?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.19,0:45:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不，是一只虫茧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No, sir. That's a bug cocoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.69,0:45:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没可能自己走进去的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}There's no way that could get way down in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.46,0:45:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,除非有人把它塞进去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Not unless somebody shoved it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.60,0:45:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把她翻过来会较易采指纹\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}She'll be easier to print when we turn her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.00,0:45:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lamar, give me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.54,0:45:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, sir, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.37,0:46:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这些是什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, Jack. What do you make of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.38,0:46:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,跟其他死者的形状不同，拍几张大特写\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Different configuration than the other victims. Get close-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.75,0:46:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,死者的皮肤...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Victim's skin removed...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.55,0:46:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在臀部以上，有两块菱形的皮肤被剥去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}in two diamond-shaped sections above the buttocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.85,0:46:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口跟第二或第三节脊骨平衡\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Exit wound level with the second or third thoracic vertebrae...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.26,0:46:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,距离右肩胛骨大约六英寸\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}approximately six inches from the right shoulder blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.33,0:46:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Starling...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.86,0:46:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我对那个警长说，我们不该在女人面前谈\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}when I told that sheriff we shouldn't talk in front of a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.57,0:46:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那令你很气恼吧？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}that burned you, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.37,0:46:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是个烟幕，我要打发他走\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It was just smoke, Starling. I had to get rid of him
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.04,0:46:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是很要紧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It matters, Mr. Crawford.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.04,0:46:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,探员们想看你怎样应付\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Cops look at you to see how to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.38,0:46:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很要紧的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.08,0:46:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Point taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.35,0:46:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,手腕周围有被捆绑的痕迹\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Ligature marks found around wrists...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.79,0:46:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,足踝就没有\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}not around the ankles.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.66,0:46:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,显示死后才剥皮的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}This would indicate that the skinning was postmortem.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.35,0:47:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,时间到了，轮到我\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Time, Pilch. My move.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.62,0:47:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-不公平，你用食物引诱它　-真无赖，仍然是轮到我\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- No fair! You lured him with produce. - Tough noogies. It's still my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.96,0:47:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝，慢慢来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Nice and slow, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.32,0:47:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,若那只甲虫推动你的棋子，也算数吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}If the beetle moves one of your men, does that still count?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.23,0:47:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,当然算数，你怎么玩的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Of course it counts. How do you play?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.60,0:47:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳探员？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Agent Starling?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.70,0:47:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西从哪里来的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Where the heck did this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.77,0:47:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,它粘糊糊的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It's practically mush.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.57,0:47:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个被杀死者身上找到的，尸体在埃尔克河里\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It was found in a murder victim. The body was in the Elk River.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.01,0:47:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是水牛比尔干的吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It's Buffalo Bill, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.68,0:47:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能透露\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I can't tell you any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.21,0:47:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在电台听到\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We heard it on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.62,0:47:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一宗真实谋杀案的线索？酷\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You mean this is a clue from a real murder case? Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.12,0:47:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,别管他，他是无名小卒\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Just ignore him. He's not a Ph.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.16,0:48:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小角天蛾，可能是...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sphingid Ceratomia, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.09,0:48:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它是只大吸血鬼\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Boy, he's a big sucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.53,0:48:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.03,0:48:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,查看一下形态学\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}let's check morphology.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.87,0:48:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳探员，你不查案时会做什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What do you do when you're not detecting, Agent Starling?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.88,0:48:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,做个学生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Try to be a student, Dr. Pilcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.95,0:48:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你去过吃起司汉堡和喝啤酒吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You ever go out for cheeseburgers and beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.75,0:48:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那有趣的招牌酒？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The amusing house wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.79,0:48:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,博士，你是否对我有意？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Are you hitting on me, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.46,0:48:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-是的　-找到了！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Yes. - Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.53,0:48:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What do you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.59,0:48:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳探员，这个是阴间冥河\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Agent Starling, meet Mr. Acherontia Styx.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.66,0:48:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.97,0:48:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,认识它的人多叫它做骷髅飞蛾\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Better known to his friends as the Death's-head moth.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.37,0:48:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它从哪里来的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Where does it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.74,0:48:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是古怪之处，它们只活在亚洲\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That's what's strange. They only live in Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.91,0:48:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是从进口的卵子繁殖的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They're specially raised from imported eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.74,0:48:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有人饲养这只东西，喂它吃蜜糖和茄类植物\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Somebody grew this guy. Fed him honey and nightshade.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.31,0:48:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给它保暖\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Kept him warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.88,0:49:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有人很爱护它\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Somebody loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.79,0:49:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.72,0:49:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,放我出去！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.20,0:49:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.63,0:49:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,救我！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.77,0:49:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,求你救我\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Help me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.11,0:49:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛你不答我？求求你！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Why won't you answer me?! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.65,0:50:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-各位早，我是唐娜・佛鲁兹　-我是报导体育的金・凯素\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Good morning. I'm Donna Ferucchi. - I'm Gene Cassel with sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.08,0:50:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是提姆・兰汉，今早的头条新闻如下\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And I'm Tim Langhorn. Our top story this morning:
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.42,0:50:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁参议员的25岁女儿凯瑟琳・马丁...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Catherine Martin, the 25-year-old daughter of Senator Ruth Martin...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.89,0:50:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一度被列为失踪人士\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}listed as a missing person...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.42,0:50:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,相信她已经被称为“水牛比尔”的杀手绑架\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}is believed to have been kidnapped by the killer known as "Buffalo Bill."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.13,0:50:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,孟斐斯市警方说，已确认出该名失踪女孩的衬衫\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Memphis police say the missing girl's blouse has been identified...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.77,0:50:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它后面被割破，案情耐人寻味\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}sliced up the back, in what has become a kind of grim calling card.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.10,0:50:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳是田纳西州的共和党...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Young Catherine is the only daughter of U.S. Senator Ruth Martin...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.68,0:50:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁参议员的独生女\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}the Republican senator from Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.91,0:50:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这宗绑架案没有政治动机\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And while her kidnapping is not considered politically motivated...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.75,0:50:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但政府高层仍然相当重视\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}it has stirred the government to its highest levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.88,0:50:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,正在佛蒙特州滑雪的总统\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Reached for comment on the ski slopes of Vermont...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.89,0:50:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,接受访问时表示，“极度关注”事件\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}the president himself said to be, and I quote, "intensely concerned."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.66,0:50:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁参议员于较早前，录影了以下的呼吁\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Just moments ago, Senator Martin taped this dramatic personal plea:
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.46,0:50:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我向挟持小女的人说话\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm speaking, now, to the person holding my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.37,0:51:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳是非常温文和善良的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Catherine is very gentle and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.24,0:51:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟她谈谈就知道\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Talk to her and you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.91,0:51:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你有力量，你有控制权\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You have the power. You are in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.45,0:51:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你感受到爱和善心的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I know you can feel love and compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.15,0:51:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你有一个向全世界展示的大好机会...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You have a wonderful chance to show the whole world...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.12,0:51:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你是善良而坚强的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}that you can be merciful, as well as strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.79,0:51:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你有能力善待凯瑟琳...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That you're big enough to treat Catherine better...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.76,0:51:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,比这个世界待你更好\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}than the world has treated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.00,0:51:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你有此能力\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You have that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.93,0:51:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,求你，我的女儿是凯瑟琳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Please. My daughter is Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.64,0:51:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是聪明\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Boy, that's smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.91,0:51:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很聪明\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Jesus, that's really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.61,0:51:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她不断重复那个名字\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}She keeps repeating the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.78,0:51:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,若他视凯瑟琳为一个人而非物件，就难以下毒手\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}If he sees Catherine as a person, not an object, it's harder to tear her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.55,0:51:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,求你放了我的女儿\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Please, release my little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.55,0:51:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳小姐，你来我的医院干什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What you're doing, Ms. Starling, is coming into my hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.32,0:51:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,并第三次拒绝跟我分享资料\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and refusing to share information with me for the third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.20,0:52:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这不过是赖普案的例行后续\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sir, I told you this is just a routine follow-up on the Raspail...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.90,0:52:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的病人，我有知情权\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He is my patient. I have rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.20,0:52:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.24,0:52:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳小姐，我不是个笨蛋\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Look, I am not just some turnkey, Miss Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.81,0:52:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是检察官的电话号码\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}This is the number for the U.S. Attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.28,0:52:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,请你跟他谈，或者让我执行任务，明白吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Please, either discuss it with him or let me do my job, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.12,0:52:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的分析能帮助我们抓到水牛比尔...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}If your profile helps us catch Buffalo Bill...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.49,0:52:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,及时救出凯瑟琳・马丁...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}in time to save Catherine Martin...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.33,0:52:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,参议员答应把你转送到...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}the senator promises you a transfer to the VA Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.03,0:52:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,它位于纽约奥尼达公园，可看到附近的园林景色的医院\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}at Oneida Park, New York, with a view of the woods nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.67,0:52:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,当然仍是高度设防的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Maximum security still applies, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.80,0:52:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以阅读书籍\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You'd have reasonable access to books.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.24,0:52:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,最好的是...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Best of all, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.54,0:52:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你每年可以离开医院一周\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}one week of the year, you get to leave the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.78,0:52:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,去这里\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and go here:
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.69,0:52:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,普拉姆岛\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Plum Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.56,0:53:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在那一星期里，你都可以在沙滩漫步\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Every day of that week, you may walk on the beach
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.96,0:53:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也可以在海中畅泳一小时\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You may swim in the ocean for up to one hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.36,0:53:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是受特种部队的监视\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}under SWAT team surveillance, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.17,0:53:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,给你的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.10,0:53:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,水牛比尔的档案副本\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}A copy of the Buffalo Bill case file.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.31,0:53:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,参议员的建议书副本\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}A copy of the senator's offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.94,0:53:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这个建议是无商讨余地的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}This offer is non-negotiable and final.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.92,0:53:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳・马丁死了你就一无所得\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Catherine Martin dies, you get nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.83,0:53:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,普拉姆岛动物病症研究中心\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Plum Island Animal Disease Research Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.13,0:53:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,听来很吸引\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sounds charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.47,0:53:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个岛有一流的海滩\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That's only part of the island. There's a very nice beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.31,0:53:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,岛上有燕鸥巢，有漂亮的...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Terns nest there. There's beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.74,0:53:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,燕鸥？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Terns?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.85,0:53:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我帮你，也会是我们的转机\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}If I help you, Clarice, it will be "turns" with us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.12,0:54:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们互相交换资料吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Quid pro quo. I tell you things, you tell me things.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.42,0:54:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是关于这宗案件，是关于你自己\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Not about this case, though. About yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.29,0:54:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,交换，好不好？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Quid pro quo. Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.76,0:54:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗？克丽丝，可怜的凯瑟琳在等着\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes or no, Clarice? Poor little Catherine is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.50,0:54:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Go, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.10,0:54:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你最糟的童年记忆是什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What is your worst memory of childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.67,0:54:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,家父去世\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The death of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.21,0:54:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我，别说谎，我会知道的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Tell me about it. And don't lie, or I'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.35,0:54:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他是镇上的警长\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He was a town marshal...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.78,0:54:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有一晚他遇上两个，从药房走出来的窃匪\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and one night he surprised two burglars coming out of a drugstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.82,0:54:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们向他开枪\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.89,0:54:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他当场死亡？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Was he killed outright?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.33,0:54:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，他很坚强，熬了个几个月\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No, he was very strong. He lasted more than a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.60,0:54:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲在我年幼时去世\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}My mother died when I was very young, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.14,0:54:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,自始父亲就成为我的一切\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}my father had become the whole world to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.44,0:55:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他离开后，我一无所有，我那时十岁\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and when he left me, I had nothing. I was 10 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.55,0:55:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你很坦白\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You're very frank, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.55,0:55:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信私底下结识你，会很有意思的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I think it would be quite something to know you in private life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.22,0:55:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,交换资料\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Quid pro quo, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.12,0:55:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谈谈西维州小姐吧，她是否身材肥大？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}So tell me about Miss West Virginia. Was she a large girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.43,0:55:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.47,0:55:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大屁股，肉团团？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Big through the hips, roomy?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.07,0:55:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,死者们全都是\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They all were.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.10,0:55:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么线索？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.47,0:55:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她的喉咙被异物塞住\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}She had an object deliberately inserted into her throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.48,0:55:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有正式公布的，我们不知道它有何意思\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Now, that hasn't been made public yet. We don't know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.21,0:55:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一只蝴蝶？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Was it a butterfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.25,0:55:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，一只飞蛾\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes. A moth.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.52,0:55:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一小时前，我们在班哲文・赖普的头颅内也找到\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Just like the one we found in Benjamin Raspail's head an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.19,0:55:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,为何他把它们放进去？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Why does he place them there, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.13,0:55:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,飞蛾的特点是转变\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The significance of the moth is change.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.90,0:55:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,幼虫变成蝶蛹或者蛹\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Caterpillar into chrysalis, or pupa...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.94,0:56:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再变成美丽的蝴蝶\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and from thence into beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.87,0:56:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔也想转变\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Our Billy wants to change too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.58,0:56:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,变性癖和暴力之间是没有关连的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}There's no correlation between transsexualism and violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.91,0:56:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-变性癖者是很被动的　-很聪明\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Transsexuals are very passive. - Clever girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.38,0:56:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你有捉拿到他的本领，知道吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You're so close to the way you're gonna catch him. Do you realize that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.85,0:56:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道，为什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No. Tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.62,0:56:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲被杀后你成了孤儿，后来怎么样？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}After your father's murder you were orphaned. What happened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.30,0:56:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,答案并非在那双廉价鞋子上\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I don't imagine the answer is on those second-rate shoes, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.67,0:56:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我去了蒙大拿州，跟我母亲的表妹夫妇同住\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I went to live with my mother's cousin and her husband in Montana.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.77,0:56:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有一个牧场\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They had a ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.71,0:56:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,牧牛场？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Was it a cattle ranch?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.48,0:56:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,牧羊和马\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sheep and horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.68,0:56:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里住了多久？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}How long did you live there?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.18,0:56:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,两个月\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.65,0:56:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,为何时间这么短？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Why so briefly?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.35,0:56:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我跑掉了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.92,0:56:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？牧场主人逼你口交？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Why, Clarice? Did the rancher make you perform fellatio?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.99,0:56:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他有没有鸡奸你？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Did he sodomize you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.59,0:57:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，他是个很正派的人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No. He was a very decent man.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.46,0:57:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,交换资料\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Quid pro quo, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.43,0:57:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔不是个真正的变性癖者\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Billy is not a real transsexual.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.00,0:57:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但他以为自己是，他想那样\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}But he thinks he is. He tries to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.11,0:57:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信他想做很多东西\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He's tried to be a lot of things, I expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.38,0:57:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我有捉拿他的本领，是何意思？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You said I was very close to the way we'd catch him. What did you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.38,0:57:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有三间主要做变性手术的中心\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}There are three major centers for transsexual surgery:
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.28,0:57:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰・霍金斯，明尼苏达州大学，和哥伦布医疗中心\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Johns Hopkins, the University of Minnesota, and Columbus Medical Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.59,0:57:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,若比尔向它们申请做变性手术，而又被拒绝...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I wouldn't be surprised if Billy applied for sex reassignment...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.09,0:57:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会感到惊讶\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}at one or all of them, and been rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.06,0:57:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们根据什么来拒绝他？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}On what basis would they reject him?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.86,0:57:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,试找寻跟暴力有关的童年创伤吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Look for severe childhood disturbances associated with violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.57,0:57:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔并非天生是个罪犯\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Our Billy wasn't born a criminal, Clarice...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.67,0:57:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是经过多年来惯常的，虐待所导致的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}he was made one through years of systematic abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.88,0:57:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他讨厌自己的身份\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Billy hates his own identity, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.51,0:57:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他以为那是令他成为变性癖者的原因\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and he thinks that makes him a transsexual...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.48,0:57:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但他的病征要更凶残...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}but his pathology is a thousand times more savage...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.82,0:57:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,和可怕千倍\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and more terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.69,0:58:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,它涂润肤液在身上，它听到指示总会依着做\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It rubs the lotion on its skin. It does this whenever it's told.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.46,0:58:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，我的家人会付钱的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Mister, my family will pay cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.43,0:58:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你要多少赎金，他们都会付\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Whatever ransom you're asking for, they'll pay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.30,0:58:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,它涂润肤液在身上，否则又要挨打了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It rubs the lotion on its skin or else it gets the hose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.88,0:58:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，珍宝，她会挨打的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, she will, Precious. She'll get the hose.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.41,0:58:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.22,0:58:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我做吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.25,0:58:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.89,0:58:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，如果你放我走，我答应不会起诉你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Mister, if you let me go, I won't press charges. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.23,0:58:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈是个重要人物\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}See, my mom is a real important woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.93,0:58:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,相信你也知道吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I guess you already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.13,0:58:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,它把润肤液放在篮里\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Now it places the lotion in the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.57,0:58:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.50,0:58:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你，我想回家\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Please, I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.37,0:58:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我想回家！求求你！放我吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I want to go home! Please! Please let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.68,0:58:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,把润肤液放在篮里\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It places the lotion in the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.98,0:59:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见我妈妈，求你放我吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I want to see my mommy. Please let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.85,0:59:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我想再见到我妈妈，我想...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I want to see my mom again. I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.82,0:59:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见我妈妈\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I want to see my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.13,0:59:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,把那他妈的润肤液放在篮里！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Put the fucking lotion in the basket!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.50,0:59:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你仍然以为可在沙滩漫步，和看鸟儿吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You still think you're gonna walk on some beach and see the birdies?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.67,0:59:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不会了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.50,0:59:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我找过凯瑟琳・马丁参议员\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I called Senator Ruth Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.91,1:00:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她没听过跟你有任何协议\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}She never heard of any deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.48,1:00:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他们骗你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They scammed you, Hannibal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.51,1:00:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Stand outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.45,1:00:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,把门关上\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And shut the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.35,1:00:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,巴尼\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Barney.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.76,1:00:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,从没有跟马丁参议员作过协议，但现在有了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}There never was a deal with Senator Martin, but there is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.23,1:00:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是我议定的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I designed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.67,1:00:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，我也为自己的利益，定下了一些条件\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Of course, I worked in a few conditions for my own benefit as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.64,1:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,说出水牛比尔的名字\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Identify Buffalo Bill by name...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.91,1:00:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那个女孩及时被发现\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and if the girl is found in time...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.18,1:00:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你就会被转送到田纳西州的丛树山州立监狱\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}you'll be transferred to Brushy Mountain State Prison in Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.55,1:00:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Answer me, Hannibal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.38,1:00:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在回答我\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You answer me now...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.45,1:00:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,否则，天啊，你休想离开这个牢房\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}or, by God, you'll never leave this cell.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.02,1:00:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,水牛比尔是谁？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Who is Buffalo Bill?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.13,1:00:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字是路易斯\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}His first name is Louis.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.73,1:00:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,其余的我只会在田纳西州，亲自对参议员说\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'll tell the rest to the Senator herself, but only in Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.50,1:01:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有几个条件\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And I have a few conditions of my own.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.57,1:01:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,替他梳洗一下，准备出发\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Clean him up and get him ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.71,1:01:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克，汉尼拔・莱达正被转送往孟斐斯途中\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Jack, Hannibal Lecter is being transferred to Memphis.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.15,1:01:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,转送？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Transferred?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.78,1:01:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你可有个见习生，冒参议员之名，向莱达提出一个虚假的建议？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Did you have a trainee make a phony offer to Lecter in the senator's name?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.29,1:01:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的主意，我逼不得已\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I rolled the dice. I had to.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.32,1:01:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她气疯了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Well, she's mad as hell, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.56,1:01:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,司法部的保罗・肯度拿来了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Paul Krendler's here from Justice.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.69,1:01:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她要求他在孟斐斯接手\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}She's asking him to take over in Memphis.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.07,1:01:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,（孟斐斯市国际机场）
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.15,1:01:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生，欢迎到孟斐斯\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Welcome to Memphis, Dr. Lecter.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.22,1:01:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是鲍尔探员，这位是派屈克警长\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm Lieutenant Boyle. This is Sergeant Patrick.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.06,1:01:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会像你待我们那么好的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We'll treat you as good as you treat us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.36,1:02:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你乖乖的，就会得到舒服的待遇\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You be a gentleman, you'll get three hots and a cot.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.50,1:02:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，请在这里签名，我们作合法的移交\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sir, if you sign right here, we'll have us a legal transfer.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.71,1:02:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Here, sir, use mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.59,1:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁参议员\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Senator Martin...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.96,1:03:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,汉尼拔・莱达医生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Hannibal Lecter.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.83,1:03:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Lecter...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.90,1:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我带了一份宣誓书，保证你新的权利\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}l've brought an affidavit guaranteeing your new rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.64,1:03:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在我签署前你要看看的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You'll want to read it before I sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.78,1:03:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会为了小利益，而耽误你或凯瑟琳的时间\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I won't waste your time or Catherine's time bargaining for petty privileges.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.21,1:03:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽丝・史达琳和克劳福，已经浪费了太多时间\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Clarice Starling and Jack Crawford have wasted too much time already.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.08,1:03:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿他们没有害死，那个可怜的女孩\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I only pray they haven't doomed the poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.72,1:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让我帮你吧，事成后我会信任你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Let me help you now. I will trust you when it is all over.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.46,1:03:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应你，保罗\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You have my word. Paul.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.23,1:03:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,水牛比尔的真名是路易斯・法兰\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Buffalo Bill's real name is Louis Friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.03,1:03:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我只见过他一次，1980年4 5月间由我的病人...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I met him just once. He was referred to me in April or May, 1980...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.21,1:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,班哲文・赖普转介给我的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}by my patient Benjamin Raspail.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.08,1:03:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是爱人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They were lovers, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.38,1:03:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但赖普变得很害怕\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}But Raspail had become very frightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.55,1:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看来路易斯谋杀了一个流浪汉\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Apparently, Louis had murdered a transient...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.75,1:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,用他的皮肤做了一些东西\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and done things with the skin.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.49,1:04:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要他的地址和容貌特征\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We need his address and a physical description.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.33,1:04:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我，参议员...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Tell me, senator.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.63,1:04:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有亲自哺育凯瑟琳？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Did you nurse Catherine yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.50,1:04:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么？　-你有没有给她喂奶？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- What? - Did you breast-feed her?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.33,1:04:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-混帐　-我有的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Now, wait a minute! - Yes. I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.00,1:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,令你的乳头变得坚挺，是吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Toughened your nipples, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.31,1:04:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个混蛋！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.81,1:04:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,把人的腿切除，他仍感到振奋\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Amputate a man's leg, and he can still feel it tickling.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.85,1:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我，妈妈，当你的小女儿被杀时\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Tell me, Mom, when your little girl is on the slab...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.35,1:04:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪里会感到振奋？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}where will it tickle you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.75,1:04:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个畜生带回巴尔的摩\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Take this thing back to Baltimore.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.09,1:04:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,五英尺十英寸，身材魁悟，约一百八十磅\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Five-foot-ten, strongly built, about 180 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.26,1:04:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,金发，浅蓝色眼睛\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hair, blond. Eyes, pale blue.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.03,1:04:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在大约三十五岁\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He'd be about 35 now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.46,1:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他声称住在费城，可能是说谎\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He said he lived in Philadelphia but may have lied.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.57,1:04:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我只记得这么多了，妈\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That's all I can remember, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.50,1:04:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,若我再想起什么，我会通知你的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}But if I think of any more, I will let you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.64,1:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,参议员，还有一件事\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, and senator, just one more thing:
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.44,1:05:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的套装很漂亮\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Love your suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.38,1:05:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,与马丁参议员，在今天较早前的会面中\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}In a meeting earlier today with Senator Ruth Martin...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.55,1:05:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生同意协助追缉水牛比尔\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Lecter agreed to help in the investigation to find Buffalo Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.58,1:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,（谢尔比县法院大楼）
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.19,1:05:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-你扮演什么角色？　-我对莱达医生的...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- How do you fit in? - My unique insight...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.36,1:05:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,独特触觉促成了这次突破\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}into Lecter made the breakthrough.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.50,1:05:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,水牛比尔叫什么名字？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Buffalo Bill's name?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.76,1:05:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这是目前有关当局的秘密\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}His name is now a matter of record with the proper authorities.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.77,1:05:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-可否给我们...　-我是奇顿医生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Can you give us...? - I'm Dr. Frederick Chilton.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.44,1:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎样写法？　-奇特的奇...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Spell it? - That's C-H...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.67,1:05:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是奇顿医生的组员吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Are you with Dr. Chilton's group?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.88,1:05:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚在外面见到他\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Well, I just saw him outside, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.58,1:05:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不能有太多人接近莱达，我们接到死亡恐吓\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Access to Lecter is limited. We've received death threats.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.05,1:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I understand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.76,1:05:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,登记和把武器放下\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Log in and check your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.83,1:05:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能独自邀功的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I can't take all the credit myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.26,1:05:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁参议员，司法部，联邦调查局\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Senator Martin, Justice Department, FBI...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.76,1:05:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,巴尔的摩州立医院的人员，最困难就是...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}folks at the Baltimore State Hospital. Now for the hard part:
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.40,1:06:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,逮捕那个疑匪\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Apprehending the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.70,1:06:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，我要赶飞机了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Excuse me, I have to catch a flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.01,1:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥台，我是杰各警员\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Command desk, Officer Jacobs.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.08,1:06:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,（路易斯・法兰飞禽，猥亵）
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.79,1:06:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,（铁）
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.15,1:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们说的是事实吗？　-什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Is it true what they're saying? - Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.23,1:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个吸血殭尸？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He's some kind of vampire?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.53,1:06:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有替他取名\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They don't have a name for what he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.83,1:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐，你知道规矩的吧？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You do know the rules, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.27,1:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,知道，我以前盘问过他\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, I've questioned him before.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.11,1:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.61,1:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽丝，晚安\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Good evening, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.15,1:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能想要回你的画吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I thought you might like your drawings back.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.52,1:07:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你有自己的景观\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Just until you get your view.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.26,1:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真是周到\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}How very thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.43,1:07:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还是在你们破案前，克劳福派你来...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Or did Jack Crawford send you for one last wheedle...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.43,1:07:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说最后一次的花言巧语？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}before you're both booted off the case?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.17,1:07:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不，是我自己想来的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No. I came because I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.07,1:07:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,人家会说我们在恋爱呢\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}People will say we're in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.65,1:07:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,安克斯岛\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Anthrax Island.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.35,1:07:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真是有心思，克丽丝\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That was an especially nice touch, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.52,1:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你画的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.22,1:08:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.46,1:08:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.66,1:08:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That was good.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.66,1:08:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但我同情可怜的凯瑟琳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Pity about poor Catherine, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.80,1:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,滴答...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Ticktock, ticktock, ticktock.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.03,1:08:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你的字谜有破绽了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Your anagrams are showing, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.67,1:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,路易斯・法兰？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Louis Friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.90,1:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是硫化铁，也叫做黄铜铁\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Iron sulfide, also known as fool's gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.54,1:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽丝，你的毛病是，你要活得轻松一点\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, Clarice, your problem is, you need to get more fun out of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.91,1:08:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你在巴尔的摩时说了真话\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You were telling me the truth back in Baltimore, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.08,1:08:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,现在继续吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Please continue now.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.15,1:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过那些档案了，你看过吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Well, I've read the case files. Have you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.02,1:08:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你要缉拿他的资料都在里面\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Everything you need to find him is there in those pages.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.29,1:08:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-那么教我怎样做　-首要的原则\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Then tell me how. - First principles, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.39,1:08:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是简易，读马可・奥勒利乌斯吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Simplicity. Read Marcus Aurelius.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.70,1:08:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,凡事都问：它是什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Of each particular thing, ask: What is it in itself?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.37,1:08:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,它有什么本质？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What is its nature?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.60,1:08:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你寻找的这个人，他做什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What does he do, this man you seek?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.01,1:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,杀害女人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He kills women.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.44,1:08:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不，那是次要的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No. That is incidental.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.91,1:09:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他主要是做什么？他杀人是为了满足什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What is the principle thing he does? What needs does he serve by killing?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.08,1:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,愤怒\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Anger...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.95,1:09:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,社会认同和性困惑\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}social acceptance and sexual frustration...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.19,1:09:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不是！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.76,1:09:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他贪图\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He covets.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.66,1:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他的本性\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That is his nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.23,1:09:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎样才会开始贪图？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And how do we begin to covet, Clarice?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.83,1:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是否去寻找贪图的东西？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Do we seek out things to covet?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.07,1:09:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,尝试回答吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Make an effort to answer now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.17,1:09:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，我们只是...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No, we just...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.84,1:09:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看见日常的东西就开始贪图\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No, we begin by coveting what we see every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.38,1:09:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你可有感到一些眼睛在盯着你？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Don't you feel eyes moving over your body, Clarice?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.42,1:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛，又可有寻找你要的东西？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And don't your eyes seek out the things you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.52,1:09:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有的，请你告诉我吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}All right, yes. Now, please tell me how.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.06,1:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.26,1:09:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到你告诉我了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It is your turn to tell me, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.43,1:09:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你再没有假期可哄骗我了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You don't have any more vacations to sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.56,1:09:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为何你离开那个牧场？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Why did you leave that ranch?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.37,1:09:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有时间再玩这一套了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Doctor, we don't have any more time for any of this now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.60,1:09:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们的时间观念是不同的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}But we don't reckon time the same way, do we?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.34,1:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有这么多的时间\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}This is all the time you'll have.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.41,1:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,稍后吧，请听着，我们只有五个...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Later. Please listen. We've only got five...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.78,1:10:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我现在要听\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No! I will listen now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.18,1:10:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲被杀后，你十岁就成了孤儿\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Your father's murder orphaned you when you were 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.35,1:10:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你去了蒙大拿，跟一些养羊马的表亲同住，之后呢？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You went to live with cousins on a sheep and horse ranch in Montana. And?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.46,1:10:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我在一个早上跑掉了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And one morning I just ran away.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.43,1:10:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的，什么驱使你离开？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Not "just," Clarice. What set you off?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.13,1:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你在什么时候出发？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You started at what time?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.47,1:10:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很早，天还没亮\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Early, still dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.97,1:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西吵醒你，是不是一个梦？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Then something woke you. Was it a dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.77,1:10:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.41,1:10:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到一种奇怪的声音\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I heard a strange noise.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.41,1:10:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.35,1:10:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It was...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.82,1:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,尖叫声\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}screaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.89,1:10:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,像小孩的尖叫声\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Some kind of screaming, like a child's voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.16,1:10:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么做？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.16,1:10:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我下楼\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I went...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.69,1:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走出屋外\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}downstairs. Outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.53,1:11:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我偷进了壳仓\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I crept up into the barn.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.34,1:11:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我很害怕看进去，但又必须看\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I was so scared to look inside, but I had to.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.67,1:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见什么？克丽丝？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And what did you see, Clarice? What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.41,1:11:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一些羔羊\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lambs.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.91,1:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它们在尖叫\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They were screaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.15,1:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在宰杀那些羔羊？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They were slaughtering the spring lambs?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.49,1:11:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而它们在尖叫\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And they were screaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.56,1:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就跑掉了？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And you ran away?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.46,1:11:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，最初我想释放它们\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No. First I tried to free them.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.96,1:11:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我打开它们的闸门\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I opened the gate to their pen.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.60,1:11:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它们只是站在那里，很困惑的，不肯走\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They just stood there, confused. They wouldn't run.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.23,1:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但你可以走，你也走了，是不是？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}But you could and you did, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.54,1:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我抱起一只羊就拔足逃跑\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes. I took one lamb and I ran away as fast as I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.14,1:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪里？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Where were you going, Clarice?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.14,1:11:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道，我没有食物和水\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I don't know. I didn't have any food, any water...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.35,1:11:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,而且当时很冷，非常冷\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and it was very cold. It was very cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.19,1:11:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I thought...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.22,1:11:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为，至少可救到一只羊\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I thought if I could save just one...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.79,1:11:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但它很重\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}but he was so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.49,1:12:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很重\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He was so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.30,1:12:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我走不了几里路，警长的车就把我截住\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I didn't get more than a few miles when the sheriffs car picked me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.41,1:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,牧场主人很生气，把我送到博斯曼的路德会孤儿院\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The rancher was so angry he sent me to a Lutheran orphanage in Bozeman.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.45,1:12:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我再没看过那个牧场了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I never saw the ranch again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.15,1:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你的羊又怎么样？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What became of your lamb, Clarice?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.82,1:12:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把它杀了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.49,1:12:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有时你仍会惊醒，是吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You still wake up sometimes, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.02,1:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在黑暗中醒来...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Wake up in the dark...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.39,1:12:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,听到那些羔羊的尖叫声？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and hear the screaming of the lambs?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.83,1:12:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.43,1:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信如果把凯瑟琳救了出来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And you think if you save poor Catherine...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.44,1:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可以令它们停止尖叫是吗？你相信如果凯瑟琳活着...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}you can make them stop, don't you? You think if Catherine lives...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.21,1:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不会在黑夜中...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}you won't wake up in the dark ever again...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.61,1:12:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,再被那些恐怖的羊声惊醒了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}to that awful screaming of the lambs.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.65,1:12:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.75,1:12:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.79,1:13:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，克丽丝\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.39,1:13:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.26,1:13:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我他的名字\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Tell me his name, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.20,1:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是奇顿医生吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Chilton, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.07,1:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你们是认识的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I think you know each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.87,1:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.04,1:13:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们找到她了　-我们走吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- We found her. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.38,1:13:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，轮到你了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It's your turn, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.55,1:13:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-出去　-说出他的名字\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Out! - Tell me his name.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.41,1:13:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我接到命令，要把你送上飞机\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sorry, ma'am, I've got orders to put you on a plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.45,1:13:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.89,1:13:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的克丽丝\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Brave Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.19,1:13:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那些羔羊停止尖叫时，你会告诉我的，是吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You will let me know when those lambs stop screaming, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.96,1:13:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,说出他的名字\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Tell me his name, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.99,1:13:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽丝\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Clarice!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.70,1:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你的档案\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Your case file.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.13,1:13:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.40,1:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再见，克丽丝\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Goodbye, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.07,1:14:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，准备好就来吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Ready when you are, doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.24,1:15:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一会\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Just another minute, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.18,1:15:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个混蛋竟然要再吃晚饭\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Son of a bitch demanded a second dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.82,1:15:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还要极生的羊排\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lamb chops, extra rare.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.86,1:15:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不知他早餐要吃什么？动物园里的怪物？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Wonder what he wants for breakfast? Some damn thing from the zoo?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.70,1:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,（化学喷雾）
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.01,1:15:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,两位，晚安\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Good evening, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.95,1:15:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，医生，蹲下吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay, doc. Grab some floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.85,1:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,跟以前的程序一样\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Same drill as before, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.76,1:15:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,庞毕探员，准备好了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Ready when you are, Sergeant Pembry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.68,1:16:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,行了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.49,1:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,递给我吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hand me that, would you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.69,1:16:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.77,1:16:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,请小心那些画\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Mind the drawings, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.00,1:16:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.60,1:17:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,庞毕，小心，他把我扣住\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Pembry, watch it, he's cuffed me!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.84,1:17:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.12,1:18:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,庞毕探员，准备好就来吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Ready when you are, Sergeant Pembry.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.00,1:18:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟什么回事？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What is this shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.40,1:18:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有人上了五楼？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Did somebody go up on five?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.30,1:18:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-没有人上过去　-叫庞毕，叫他告诉...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- No, nobody went up. - Call Pembry. Ask him to tell...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.01,1:19:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,CP，五楼有枪声，重复，五楼有枪声\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}CP, shots fired on five. Repeat, shots fired on five.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.28,1:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,戴德警官\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sergeant Tate!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.22,1:19:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,去，五楼有枪声\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Proceed. Shots fired on five.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.42,1:19:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.29,1:19:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么了？　-混蛋！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- What the hell? - Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.46,1:19:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.73,1:19:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,波比，拿避弹衣来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Bobby, get the vest.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.09,1:19:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是，警官\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Right, sarge.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.90,1:19:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-布莱迪，霍华，掩护　-看！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Brady, Howard, cover... - Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.90,1:19:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它停了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.70,1:19:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,封锁方圆十幢楼的范围\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Seal off a 10-block radius.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.57,1:19:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,召特种部队和救护车来，快点！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Get me the SWAT team and an ambulance, double quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.74,1:19:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们上楼去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We're going up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.94,1:19:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,庞毕？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Pembry?!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.91,1:20:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍尔？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Boyle?!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.39,1:20:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.90,1:20:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.77,1:20:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-没有人　-没有人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Clear. - Clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.37,1:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥站\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Command post.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.21,1:20:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,两个警员死了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Two officers down.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.94,1:20:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-没有人　-没有人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Clear! - Clear!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.88,1:20:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,警官，莱达不见了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lecter's gone, sarge.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.28,1:20:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,囚犯失踪了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Prisoner is missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.28,1:20:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍尔的配枪不见了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Boyle's gun is gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.09,1:20:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,重复，莱达持械失踪了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Repeat. Lecter is missing and armed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.79,1:20:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他拿走了床铺\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He stripped the bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.02,1:20:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可能用来做绳，搜查所有窗户\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Might be making a rope. Check all the windows.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.99,1:20:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,救护车在哪里？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Where the fuck is my ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.76,1:20:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他仍活着的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.33,1:20:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,戴德警官，他仍活着！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sergeant Tate! He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.50,1:21:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,扶着他，抚摸他的手，跟他说话\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Get ahold of him and feel his hands. Talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.20,1:21:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What do I say?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.44,1:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他是庞德吉姆，跟他说话，该死\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It's Jim Pembry. Now talk to him, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.28,1:21:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达持械失踪了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lecter is missing and armed.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.75,1:21:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-庞毕...你听到我吗？　-他拿了鲍尔的配枪\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Pembry. Pembry, can you hear me? - He took Boyle's gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.78,1:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,庞毕发过一枪，莱达可能中了枪的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Pembry got off one round. There's a chance Lecter's hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.02,1:21:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,继续呼吸吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Keep breathing in and out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.15,1:21:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你做得很好，你没事的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You're doing a good job. You look real good there.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.36,1:21:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对，你没事的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, you look... Look real good.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.25,1:21:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-准备了吗？　-来吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- You ready? - Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.41,1:21:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们来吧　-好的，走吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Let's do it. - Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.56,1:22:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，你支持得住的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Looking good. You're gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.90,1:22:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Everything's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.10,1:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要作静脉注射　-乳酸林格注射液\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- I need that IV now! - Lactated Ringer's.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.53,1:22:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可否拿那条带子来？氧气在哪里？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Can we get the strap? Where's the oxygen?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.10,1:22:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄，情况很好，镇定一点\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Doing good, buddy. That's right. Stay with me here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.17,1:22:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他不行了，去楼下，快点\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We're losing him! Downstairs, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.28,1:22:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And up!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.98,1:22:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-电梯！　-这边\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Elevator! - This way!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.25,1:22:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-让开！　-让开！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Out of the way! - Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.69,1:22:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,CP叫戴德\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}CP to Tate.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.46,1:22:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,收到，我是戴德\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Roger, lieutenant. Tate here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.53,1:22:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在乘电梯送庞毕下来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm on the elevator bringing Pembry down.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.63,1:22:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他看来支持得住\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He seems to be hanging on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.30,1:22:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,最高的三层楼封锁了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Top three floors secured.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.93,1:22:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,主要楼梯封锁了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Main stairwell secured.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.97,1:22:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们相信他在二楼\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We think he's on two.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.12,1:23:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,戴德，你听到吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Tate, you still with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.96,1:23:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们颇肯定他在二楼\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We're pretty sure he's somewhere on two, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.49,1:23:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,通话暂时完毕\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That's all for now. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.88,1:23:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他在电梯顶\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He's on the roof of the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.15,1:23:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，大家来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.10,1:23:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到他\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.57,1:23:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他的手旁边有一支枪，他没有动\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}There's a gun by his hand. He's not moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.77,1:23:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-警告，我们要生擒他　-知道\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- One warning. We need him alive. - Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.68,1:23:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lecter?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.21,1:24:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,把双手放在头上\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Put your hands on your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.52,1:24:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,向腿射一枪\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}One in the leg.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.06,1:24:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没有动静\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No movement.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.83,1:24:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰，不要开枪，我们要进入电梯\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Johnny, hold your fire. We're coming into the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.00,1:24:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会打开盖口\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We're opening the hatch.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.47,1:24:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小心他的手\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Watch his hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.67,1:24:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有开火，会是我们发的，确定\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}If there's any fire, it'll come from us. Affirm.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.81,1:24:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.00,1:24:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,孟斐斯医院，这是26号车\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Memphis General, this is Unit 26.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.14,1:25:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会送来一名五十岁男警\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We're inbound with a 50-year-old male officer...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.91,1:25:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他面部有严重割伤\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}with severe facial lacerations.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.24,1:25:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他全身出现抽搐，情况严重\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He had grand mal seizure activity. He's postdictal now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.58,1:25:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-收到　-重要器官情况良好\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- I copy. - Vital signs are good.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.95,1:25:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-血压是130/90　-90？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Pressure is 130l90. - Ninety?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.82,1:25:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对，是90，脉搏84\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, that's right, 90. Pulse, 84.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.25,1:25:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给他注射了乳酸林格注射液\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We got him on lactated Ringer's running...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.76,1:25:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,病人正在吸十公升的氧气\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}and the patient is on 10 liters of oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.19,1:25:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小心！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.70,1:25:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那辆救护车在孟斐斯机场一个车库里被发现\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The ambulance was found in a parking garage at Memphis Airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.30,1:25:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,工作人员死了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The crew was dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.87,1:25:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他还杀了一名游客\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He killed a tourist too.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.71,1:25:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拿了他的衣服和钞票\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Got his clothes, cash.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.98,1:25:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能在任何地方\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}By now he could be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.98,1:25:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-他不会来对付我的　-真的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- He won't come after me. - Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.18,1:25:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.78,1:25:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能解释\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I can't explain it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.75,1:25:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他认为那样做很无礼\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He would consider that rude.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.45,1:25:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,都完了，她已经死了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It's over. She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.49,1:25:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你的错\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.32,1:25:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达说，我们需要捉拿他的资料都在这里，但我不能...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lecter said everything we need to catch him with is here, only I can't...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.16,1:25:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生说了很多话\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Lecter said a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.70,1:25:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,雅戴，他在这里的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He's here, Ardelia.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.56,1:26:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是莱达的笔迹吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Is this Lecter's handwriting?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.57,1:26:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样杂乱地分布现场，不是有点极度随意吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}"Doesn't this random scattering of sites seem desperately random?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.14,1:26:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,像个差劲说谎者的精心策划？汉尼拔・莱达\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Like the elaboration of a bad liar? Ta. Hannibal Lecter."
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.14,1:26:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,“极度随意”，他是什么意思？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}"Desperately random." What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.38,1:26:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可能根本不是随意，是有一个模式的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Not random at all, maybe. Like there's a pattern here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.38,1:26:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但并没有模式，不然电脑也会发现\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}But there's no pattern or the computers would've nailed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.82,1:26:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,尸体甚至是不依次序被发现的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They're even found in random order.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.45,1:26:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不依次序是因为那个被他沈下的女孩\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Random because of the one girl. The one he weighted down.
