Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.83,1:27:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来自俄亥俄州的贝尔维迪尔\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}From Belvedere, Ohio.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.36,1:27:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,第一个遇害的女孩，尸体是第三个被发现，为什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The first girl taken, third body found. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.13,1:27:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有漂浮，他把她沈下去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}She didn't drift. He weighted her down.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.47,1:27:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达说的首要原则是什么？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What did Lecter say about the "first principles"?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.01,1:27:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,简易\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.78,1:27:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这个家伙做什么？他贪图\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What does this guy do? He covets.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.25,1:27:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎样开始贪图的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}How do we first start to covet?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.95,1:27:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们贪图见到的东西\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We covet what we see.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.85,1:27:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,每天见到的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.49,1:27:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,该死，克丽丝\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hot damn, Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.19,1:27:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他认识她的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He knew her.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.46,1:27:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,（俄亥俄州贝尔维迪尔市）
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.87,1:28:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,贝先生？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Mr. Bimmel?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.47,1:28:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.04,1:28:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，我是克丽丝・史达琳，联邦调查局探员\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hello, I'm Clarice Starling. I'm with the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.61,1:28:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,贝先生，我想四周看看\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I appreciate you letting me take a look around, Mr. Bimmel.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.35,1:29:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有什么新资料给你了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I don't know nothing new to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.68,1:29:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,警方已经来过很多次\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Police been back here so many times already.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.32,1:29:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,费迪坐巴士去芝加哥求职\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Fredrica went into Chicago on the bus to see about a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.76,1:29:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她好端端的离开面试\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}She left the interview okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.36,1:29:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就没有回家\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}She never come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.80,1:29:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她的卧房是原封不动的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Her bedroom's how she left it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.40,1:29:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在楼上\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.07,1:29:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,左边那一间\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Door to the left.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.63,1:32:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他在替自己做女装，用真的女人做\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He's making himself a woman suit. Out of real women!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.47,1:32:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他还懂得缝纫\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}And he can sew!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.74,1:32:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他很熟练，他是个裁缝或...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He's very skilled. He's a tailor or a dressmaker or...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.94,1:32:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-史达琳！　-所以她们都身材肥大\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Starling! - That's why they're big.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.91,1:32:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他让她们活着，逼使她们挨饿\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}He keeps them alive so he can starve them...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.35,1:32:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,令她们的皮肤松弛，然后...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}loosen their skin and...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.98,1:32:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳，我们知道他的身份和下落\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Starling! We know who and where he is!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.72,1:32:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快到达了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We're on our way right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.42,1:32:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-哪里？　-芝加哥卡柳梅特城\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Where? - Calumet City, edge of Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.52,1:32:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我45分钟后会和飞虎队降落\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Be on the ground in 45 minutes with HRT.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.29,1:32:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息，但怎么...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}That's great news, sir. But how...?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.69,1:32:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把约翰・霍金斯提供的名字，输入已知犯人的档案\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We fed the names Johns Hopkins came up with into Known Offenders.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.50,1:32:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫杰米・甘姆，又名约翰・格兰\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Subject's name is Jamie Gumb, a.k.a. John Grant.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.63,1:32:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达的描述是正确的，他只是捏造那个名字\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lecter's description was accurate. He just lied about the name.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.54,1:32:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,海关有些关于他的资料\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Customs had some paper on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.87,1:32:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,两年前他们在洛杉矶机场，查到一个纸箱\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}They stopped a carton two years ago at LAX.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.11,1:32:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是一些来自苏里南的活毛虫\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Live caterpillars from Suriname.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.38,1:32:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,收件人叫詹米・甘姆\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The addressee was a Jame Gumb.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.95,1:32:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,芝加哥离这里只有四百哩，我很快...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Chicago is only 400 miles from here. I'll be there in...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.05,1:33:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不，没有时间了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No, there's not enough time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.95,1:33:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要控告他谋杀，不是绑架\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We want him for murder, not kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.36,1:33:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在起诉他前，要找出他与费迪嘉・拜姆的关系\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Link him to Bimmel before he's indicted.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.83,1:33:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-你去贝尔维迪尔看有什么发现　-知道，我会尽力的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- See what you can find in Belvedere. - Yes, sir. You bet. I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.06,1:33:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Starling.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.16,1:33:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你我们就找不到他，大家都会记着这点\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We wouldn't have found him without you. Nobody will forget that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.07,1:33:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是我\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Least of all me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.74,1:33:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，长官\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.11,1:33:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，葛先生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you very much, Mr. Crawford.
