Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.66,1:33:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋，谢谢那些冷饭菜汁\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thanks for the scraps, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.26,1:33:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我有更好的主意\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I got a better idea.
