Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.77,1:34:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，珍宝，乖\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Come on, Precious. Come on, Precious.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.55,1:34:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，珍宝\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Come on, Precious.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.49,1:34:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我有好吃的点心给你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I got a yummy, yummy snack for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.56,1:34:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,来吃吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Come and get it!
