Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.12,1:37:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,当联邦密探很棒吧？要经常出门的吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Is that a good job, FBI agent? You get to travel around and stuff?
