Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.64,1:37:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到这份银行工作时，费迪很替我开心\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Freddie was so happy for me when I got this job at the bank.
