Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.47,1:37:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我和玛娜茜曾替她做利普曼太太的替工\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Me and Pam Malavesi used to help her do alterations for old Mrs. Lippman.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.74,1:37:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可以把她的地址给我吗？我要跟她谈谈\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Can I get Mrs. Lippman's address? I need to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.88,1:37:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,（伊利诺斯州卡柳梅特城）
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.41,1:38:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,太有劲了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}So powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.37,1:38:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真的漂亮\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}So beautiful.
