Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.04,1:38:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖，珍宝？你没事吧？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, poodlie-poo. Precious? Darling, are you all right?
