Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.41,1:39:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-他妈的！　-你还是给我拿电话来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Oh, fuck! - You better get me that telephone!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.85,1:39:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要动手了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm gonna do it, mister!!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.15,1:39:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我会折断它的颈，我发誓我会的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm gonna snap her neck off, I swear to God!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.69,1:39:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，先生，我要做了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}All right, mister. I'm doing it!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.28,1:40:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，我来了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.92,1:40:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们进去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We're going in.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.16,1:40:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,午安，抱歉打扰你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Good afternoon. Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.56,1:40:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我找利普曼太太的家人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm looking for Mrs. Lippman's family.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.53,1:40:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局！大家伏下！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}FBI! Everybody down!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.60,1:40:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们搬走了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Lippmans don't live here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.73,1:40:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，先生，我要跟你谈谈\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Excuse me, sir. I need to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.40,1:40:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-没有人　-没有人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Clear! - Clear!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.97,1:40:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么问题呢？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}What's the problem, officer?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.21,1:40:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在调查费迪嘉・拜姆的死因\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm investigating the death of Fredrica Bimmel.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.21,1:40:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克，这里没人\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}There's no one here, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.48,1:40:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽丝\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.85,1:40:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,阁下是...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Your name is...?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.15,1:40:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克・戈登\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, Jack Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.49,1:40:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,戈登先生，很好\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Mr. Gordon. Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.56,1:40:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,费迪是利普曼太太的雇员，你认识他吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Fredrica worked for Mrs. Lippman. Did you know her?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.79,1:40:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不认识\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No, uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.03,1:40:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.80,1:41:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她是不是身材肥胖的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Was she a great big fat person?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.90,1:41:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是，她很肥胖\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, she was a big girl, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.74,1:41:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我可能有...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, I may have...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.44,1:41:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我在报纸上读到她的新闻\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No, I read about her in the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.78,1:41:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,利普曼太太有儿子，他或许可以帮忙\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Mrs. Lippman had a son. Maybe he could help.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.35,1:41:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我这里有他的名片\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I got his card in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.28,1:41:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你要进来吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You want to come in?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.72,1:41:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以吗？　-当然可以\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- May I? - Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.02,1:41:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.04,1:41:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们很快会抓到人吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Are you close to catching somebody?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.87,1:41:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.08,1:41:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,或者吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}We may be.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.11,1:41:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Did you...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.25,1:41:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在利普曼太太死后搬到这里来？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}take over this place after Mrs. Lippman died, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.15,1:41:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我两年前买了这间屋\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, I bought this house two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.76,1:42:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她有没有留下任何记录，业务记录...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Did she leave any records, any business records...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.29,1:42:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,税单，雇员名单之类？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}tax forms, lists of employees?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.80,1:42:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，完全没有\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No, nothing like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.10,1:42:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局可有什么发现？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Say, has the FBI learned something?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.04,1:42:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的警方看来毫无头绪\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The police around here don't seem to have the first clue.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.02,1:42:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有没有容貌，指纹之类的线索？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Have you got, like, a description, fingerprints, anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.16,1:42:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.83,1:42:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No, we don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.54,1:42:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个电话号码了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Here's that number.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.51,1:42:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Very good, Mr. Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.38,1:42:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可否借用你的电话？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}May I use your phone, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.36,1:43:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sure you can use my phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.89,1:43:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,别动！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.90,1:43:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,把双手放在头上，转过来，张开腿\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Put your hands over your head and turn around. Spread your legs.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.13,1:43:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,张开腿\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Spread your legs!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.64,1:43:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,把双手放在...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Put your hands in the back...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.57,1:43:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别动！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.64,1:44:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.60,1:44:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你在吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.34,1:45:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我在下面...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm down here! I'm down here!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.66,1:45:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳・马丁？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Catherine Martin?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.49,1:45:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.56,1:45:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}FBI.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.03,1:45:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你安全了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.53,1:45:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,安全个屁！快救我出去\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Safe, shit! Get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.65,1:45:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事的，他在哪里？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You're all right. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.72,1:45:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道？快救我出去！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}How the fuck should I know? Just get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.89,1:45:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳，你静一点，叫那只狗别吵\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Catherine, you've gotta be quiet! Now, shut that dog up!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.26,1:45:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,快救我出去！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Just get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.43,1:45:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.03,1:46:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳，我会救你的，但你听着\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Catherine, I'm gonna get you out. But right now, you listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.26,1:46:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要离开一会，很快回来\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I've gotta leave. I'll be right back
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.24,1:46:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不要丢下我，你这个婊子，别走！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}No! Don't you leave me here, you fucking bitch! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.51,1:46:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要丢下我！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Don't you leave me here!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.25,1:46:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个家伙是疯的！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}This guy is fucking crazy!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.35,1:46:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，我要离开这里\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Wait! I gotta get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.69,1:46:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.89,1:46:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳！其他的探员会很快到达的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Catherine! The other officers will be here any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.80,1:46:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要走！求求你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Wait! Don't go! Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.73,1:46:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别吵！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.34,1:46:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, God! Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.94,1:50:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,（恐怖）
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.71,1:50:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,（比尔剥下第五个人的皮）
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.84,1:50:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-你没事吧？　-小事，不要紧，我没事\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- You okay? - Gunpowder. It's nothing, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.51,1:50:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳探员，你怎么追查到水牛比尔在这里的？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Agent Starling, how did you track Buffalo Bill here?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.75,1:50:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,（司法部联邦调查局）
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.85,1:50:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽丝・史达琳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Clarice M. Starling.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.89,1:50:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.71,1:51:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,昂利・史蒂文\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Ernest W. Stevens.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.23,1:51:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,特种探员克丽丝・史达琳！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Special Agent Starling!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.53,1:51:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-特种探员麦普　-有电话找你\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- Special Agent Mapp. - Phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.67,1:51:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，失陪\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.20,1:51:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Starling.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.31,1:51:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,替我们拍照好吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Pilch, could you take our picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.41,1:51:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.41,1:51:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想说声恭喜\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I just wanted to say congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.91,1:51:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不擅应酬，所以我要走了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I'm no good at this kind of thing, so I'm gonna duck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.95,1:51:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Okay. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.09,1:51:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，葛先生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you, Mr. Crawford.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.56,1:52:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,令尊今天定会很骄傲\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Your father would've been proud today.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.10,1:52:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了接听电话\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Don't forget your phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.48,1:52:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,史达琳\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Starling.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.08,1:52:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽丝...\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Well, Clarice...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.21,1:52:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那些羔羊停止尖叫了吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}have the lambs stopped screaming?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.15,1:52:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Lecter?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.48,1:52:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不必追踪这个电话，我不会讲太久\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Don't bother with a trace. I won't be on long enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.02,1:52:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生，你在哪里？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Where are you, Dr. Lecter?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.36,1:52:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不打算找你了\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I have no plans to call on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.43,1:52:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有了你，这个世界更加有趣\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The world's more interesting with you in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.43,1:52:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你保重，日后报答我吧\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}So you take care now to extend me the same courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.63,1:52:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能作那个承诺的\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}You know I can't make that promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.67,1:52:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿我们可以多聊一会\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}I do wish we could chat longer...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.34,1:52:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我找了个老朋友吃晚饭\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}but I'm having an old friend for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.51,1:52:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.25,1:52:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生！\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Lecter!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.08,1:52:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Lecter.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.72,1:53:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Lecter.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.12,1:53:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,莱达医生？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Lecter?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.73,1:53:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，对不起\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}Excuse me. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.33,1:53:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,保安系统安排了吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}The security system's set up?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.20,1:53:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们有严密保安的　-谢谢\N{\fntahoma\fs13\1c&H0080FF&}- We have the big shot security. - I appreciate it.

